# Demo Images Storage

When generating or saving demonstration images (diagrams, concept art, screenshots for documentation):

- **Save to:** `E:\demo_images\` (or `E:\` root)
- **Do NOT save to:** C drive paths (e.g. `C:\Users\...`, `%APPDATA%`, etc.) — user's C drive is full
- Project workspace is on E drive; prefer E: for any generated assets meant for demonstration
